viewData.name: PhiBrows Brown 1 SUPE Pigment 5ml - 2pcs
viewData.short_description: Brown 1 is a light pigment used with natural blondes. It can also be used with naturally brown eyebrows if the client has enough natural hairs. It is difficult to use this pigment in shading technique because it makes a very warm shade, regardless of the tools used.┬á
viewData.long_description: Brown 1 is a light pigment used with natural blondes. It can also be used with naturally brown eyebrows if the client has enough natural hairs. It is difficult to use this pigment in shading technique because it makes a very warm shade, regardless of the tools used.┬á contains 2 pieces of 5ml pigment
